metadata.name: Guardian Spirits
metadata.description:
Inspired by Indonesia's esotericism concept that a person can have multiple guardian spirits - Their guardian spirits can come from family lineage, a natural gift, random encounter, and even you can buy one (yes, that's the craziest belief). And all those guardian spirits can come in different forms that each individual believes - Angel, Demons, Djinn, Elemental spirits, etc.

I use that concept as the base for the prompt and mix it with Japanese vintage toys to show contrast and uniquely represent how it looks if you really "collect" more than one Guardian Spirits.
